#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid "Ninjutsu"
msgstr "忍术"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': 'Ninjutsu'}'
#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Ninjutsu is a traditional art of combining martial arts and tactics used by "
"ninja from the Kamakura period to the Edo period. We focus on quick and "
"accurate covert attacks. It makes the superhuman battle possible by using "
"the behavior principle of Sun Tzu Feng Shima Volcano."
msgstr ""
"忍术是从镰仓时代到江户时代忍者使用的结合武术与战术的传统技艺。我们专注于快速而精准的隐秘攻击。它通过运用孙子兵法风林火山的行为原则，使超乎常人的战斗成为可能。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Ninjutsu'}'
#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"風林火山:Swift as wind, gentle as the forest, fierce as the fire, unshakable as "
"mountain"
msgstr "风林火山：其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山"

#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid "Ninjutsu (Fire)"
msgstr "忍术（火）"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Ninjutsu (Fire)' for martial art '{'str':
#. 'Ninjutsu'}'
#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Activation condition: Attack hits \n"
" Accuracy and damage increased by 20% of Dexterity "
msgstr ""
"激活条件：攻击命中 \n"
" 命中率与伤害增加敏捷的20%"

#: .\ninja_martialarts.json
msgid "Ninjutsu (Forest)"
