#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgid "Disciple of Ninjutsu"
msgstr "忍术门徒"

#. ~ Description for Disciple of Ninjutsu
#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgid ""
"I inherited Ninjutsu from my grandfather. I usually live a life that has not"
" changed from the ordinary citizens, but I secretly practice my training and"
" I am acquiring mystery. After that we need physical strength to operate it."
msgstr "我从祖父那里继承了忍术。我通常过着与普通市民无异的生活，但私下里坚持修炼，逐渐领悟奥秘。之后我们需要体力来运用它。"

#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Ninja"
msgstr "忍者"

#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Kunoichi"
msgstr "女忍者"

#. ~ Profession (male Ninja) description
#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a disciple to Ninjutsu. The ninja occupation is no longer necessary "
"in modern times, but its skill, knowledge, and spirit have been handed down "
"in succession. It will not change even if major catastrophe occurs. Let's "
"survive in order to survive your school!"
msgstr "你是忍术的门徒。忍者职业在现代已非必需，但其技艺、知识与精神却代代相传。即便发生重大灾难也不会改变。为了传承你的流派，努力生存下去吧！"

#. ~ Profession (female Kunoichi) description
#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a disciple to Ninjutsu. The ninja occupation is no longer necessary "
"in modern times, but its skill, knowledge, and spirit have been handed down "
"in succession. It will not change even if major catastrophe occurs. Let's "
"survive in order to survive your school!"
msgstr "你是忍术的门徒。忍者职业在现代已非必需，但其技艺、知识与精神却代代相传。即便发生重大灾难也不会改变。为了传承你的流派，努力生存下去吧！"

