msgstr "女忍者（角色扮演）"

#. ~ Profession (male Ninja (Cosplay)) description
#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"I wanted to be a ninja. It seems that some serious things have happened, but"
" now is my chance. The neighbors who watch with blank white eyes don't have "
"any laws to stop me anymore.  Unfortunately the cosplay party seems to be "
"canceled."
msgstr ""
"我曾梦想成为忍者。虽然似乎发生了严重的事情，但现在正是我的机会。那些用空洞白眼看我的邻居们再也无法用法律阻止我了。可惜角色扮演派对似乎取消了。"

#. ~ Profession (female Kunoichi(Cosplay)) description
#: .\ninja_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"I wanted to be a ninja. It seems that some serious things have happened, but"
" now is my chance. The neighbors who watch with blank white eyes don't have "
"any laws to stop me anymore.  Unfortunately the cosplay party seems to be "
"canceled."
msgstr ""
"我曾梦想成为忍者。虽然似乎发生了严重的事情，但现在正是我的机会。那些用空洞白眼看我的邻居们再也无法用法律阻止我了。可惜角色扮演派对似乎取消了。"

